gion.gov.by/index.aspx?id=22 Kletsk raion page] at Minsk [[Oblispolkom]] website</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Minsk Region}}\n\n{{coord|53|03|49|N|26|38|14|E|type:adm2nd_source:kolossus-itwiki|display=title}}\n\n[[Category:Districts of Minsk Region]]\n[[Category:Kletsk District| ]]\n{{Belarus-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n|type                   = [[districts of Belarus|District]]\n|name                   = Kletsk District\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = {{lang|be|\u041a\u043b\u0435\u0446\u043a\u0456   \u0440\u0430\u0451\u043d}} {{lang|ru|\u041a\u043b\u0435\u0446\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0440\u0430\u0439\u043e\u043d}}\n|native_name_lang       = be\n|image_flag             = \n|flag_link              = \n|image_shield           = Coat of Arms of Kleck, Belarus.svg\n|shield_size            =\n|shield_link            = \n|flag_size              =\n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|subdivision_type       = \n|subdivision_name       =  \n|subdivision_type1      = [[Capital (political)|Administrative center]]\n|subdivision_name1      =  [[Kletsk]]\n|subdivision_type2      = \n|subdivision_name2      =  \n|subdivision_type3      = \n|subdivision_name3      = \n|subdivision_type4      =   \t\n|subdivision_name4      = \n|subdivision_type5      = \n|subdivision_name5      = \n|latd= |latm= |lats= |latNS= \n|longd= |longm= |longs= |longEW=\n|area_total_km2         = 974\n|population_total       = 32.100\n|population_as_of       = \n|population_density_km2 =\n|elevation_max_m            =  \n|elevation_min_m            =\n|elevation_footnotes    =\n|image_map              = Minsk-Oblast-Kletsk.png\n|image_dot_map          =\n|dot_x = |dot_y = \n|mapsize                = 200px\n|postal_code_type       = \n|postal_code            = \n|area_code              =\n|leader_title           = [[ispolkom]] 